  <svg
        ref="stageRef"
        class="h-[520px] w-full select-none rounded-md bg-neutral-50"
        role="application"
        @pointerdown="onStagePointerDown"
        @pointermove="onStagePointerMove" //is executed over 60+ times per second giving the appearance of smooth movement. The coordinates of the selected shape are continuosly updates by the ref and the final placement of the shape is saved in theis state variable. 
        @pointerup="onStagePointerUp"
        @pointerleave="onStagePointerLeave"
      >
```



